import React from 'react'
import About from './About'
import { Routes, Route} from "react-router-dom";
import Contact from './Contact'
import Services from './Services'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <>

        <Routes>
            <Route  to={<About/>} />
        </Routes>

        
        <Contact/>
        <Services/>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
